Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> start
Rule 1     start -> bloc
Rule 2     bloc -> bloc statement SEMI
Rule 3     bloc -> statement SEMI
Rule 4     statement -> PRINT LPAREN expression RPAREN
Rule 5     statement -> NAME EGAL expression
Rule 6     expression -> expression INF expression
Rule 7     expression -> expression INFEG expression
Rule 8     expression -> expression SUP expression
Rule 9     expression -> expression EGALEGAL expression
Rule 10    expression -> expression AND expression
Rule 11    expression -> expression OR expression
Rule 12    expression -> expression PLUS expression
Rule 13    expression -> expression TIMES expression
Rule 14    expression -> expression MINUS expression
Rule 15    expression -> expression DIVIDE expression
Rule 16    expression -> LPAREN expression RPAREN
Rule 17    expression -> NUMBER
Rule 18    expression -> NAME
Rule 19    statement -> IF LPAREN expression RPAREN LACC bloc RACC
Rule 20    statement -> IF LPAREN expression RPAREN LACC bloc RACC ELSE LACC bloc RACC

Terminals, with rules where they appear

AND                  : 10
DIVIDE               : 15
EGAL                 : 5
EGALEGAL             : 9
ELSE                 : 20
IF                   : 19 20
INF                  : 6
INFEG                : 7
LACC                 : 19 20 20
LPAREN               : 4 16 19 20
MINUS                : 14
NAME                 : 5 18
NUMBER               : 17
OR                   : 11
PLUS                 : 12
PRINT                : 4
RACC                 : 19 20 20
RPAREN               : 4 16 19 20
SEMI                 : 2 3
SUP                  : 8
TIMES                : 13
error                : 

Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

bloc                 : 1 2 19 20 20
expression           : 4 5 6 6 7 7 8 8 9 9 10 10 11 11 12 12 13 13 14 14 15 15 16 19 20
start                : 0
statement            : 2 3

